summary: A conversion of the Dynasty Armor by Codecrackerx9 and ken1945 for UNPB-BBP with working weight slider. It requires Codecrackerx9\'s original mod.
descriptionHtml:
A conversion of the Dynasty Armor by Codecrackerx9 and ken1945 for UNPB-BBP with working weight slider. It requires Codecrackerx9\'s original mod.

This is my third modification. Any advice will be wellcomed.

English is not my native language so sorry for my mistakes.

Update 0.2: panty closer to the body
Update 0.3: minor fixes in pelvis area, specially on lower weights

Required mods:
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/5733]Dynasty Armor[/url]
The UNPB body replacer with BBP support: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37900/]UNPB REDUX PROJECT[/url] OR [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20227/?]Troublemakers Clothing[/url]

Does not work without BBP.

Installation:
First install the required mods
Use NMM and overwrite when asked. Say no to upgrade.
Manual installation: open archive, extract meshes folder into data folder and overwrite when asked.

Credits and thanks:
Codecrackerx9 and ken1945 for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/5733]Dynasty Armor[/url]
dimon99 and calyps and xp32 for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14899]UNP BLESSED BODY UNPB - Now with Jiggle BBP[/url]
dimon99 for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url]
author: belisariu
